4.10	Mazinger_Z_(robot)	Mazinger Z (robot)	Mazinger Z is a fictional mecha from the anime and manga series of the same name, created by Go Nagai. Within the story, Mazinger Z was created by Professor Juzou Kabuto and piloted by his grandson Kouji. Mazinger Z is often credited as the first piloted robot, making it the ancestor of the wildly popular mecha genre.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/ac/MazingerMK.gif/220px-MazingerMK.gif
